{
  "stem": "5388.5",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Keep in mind, there was oil fields and-- not oil field but those kinds of plates that had oil content, and they used to press them out to unroll the mines.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I met a guard, a nice guy, a Dutchman.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He was working for the [NON-ENGLISH], that was the [NON-ENGLISH] or the construction--",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--engineers, and so forth.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So they used to bring us from the camp, and we used to work for them.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And kind of befriended with him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he gave me, I found out, Mussolini was overthrown.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "As I told you, I was all ears to find out what goes on in the world.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That he was overthrown and the king is now--",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then I got some German newspapers from him, I got a [NON-ENGLISH], which was the main organ of the Nazi party, so I could see-- I mean, I've learned to read between the lines a long time ago, so I could see what goes on in the world, which-- and so I kind of-- I said, you know what?",
      "word_count": 60
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Let's go to the farmer, I have something.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I made arrangements.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I gave the farmer the watch, and not realizing-- you know, and the earrings-- that you're not a boss yourself if you're common and so forth.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You brought this watch and earrings from Vilna ghetto?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "From Vilna.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When they gave us a loaf of bread, I opened up the loaf of bread, and I put it in and closed it.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they made a search, but it was already dark.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I was in another corner.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And low and behold, just about four or five people before me, they stopped the search.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They had to close it, otherwise, I would have maybe gotten shot altogether, OK?",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
